# Cisco Modeling Labs Web Access

This guide covers accessing the Cisco Modeling Labs web interface after the initial setup is complete.

---

# Open Web Browser

From the host machine, open a browser.

Navigate to:

```
https://CML-IP-ADDRESS
```

Example:

```
https://192.168.1.100
```

---

# Certificate Warning

The first connection may show a certificate warning.

This occurs because CML uses a self-signed certificate.

Select:

```
Advanced
> Continue to website
```

---

# Login

Use the CML user credentials created during the initial setup.

Example:

```
Username:
admin

Password:
********
```

---

# CML Dashboard

After successful login, the CML dashboard will load.

